unittitle_ssm: Constance Reid Collection of Richard Courant Oral History Interviews
abstract_ssm: Constance Reid (1918-2010) was a writer who specialized in biographies of mathematicians. The Constance Reid Collection of Richard Courant Oral History Interviews consists of oral history transcripts and some additional ephemera donated by Constance Reid to the Courant Institute Library.
